ractions, and between the leading order\nquadratic and quartic in spin interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Oct 2014 19:59:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2015 10:26:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2015 22:29:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-02"}
