y conclusion on the presence or absence of tori associated with WMAP\nselected blazars. With the latter selection blazars of all types (FSRQs with\nand without evidence of torus, BL Lacs, blazars of unknown type) occupy the\nsame region of the WISE color-color plane, and their region overlaps that of\nSDSS quasars with point-like morphology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Oct 2014 09:08:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
